ow a log normal distribution which\nreminds of the same behavior already found in traditional software systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Feb 2018 17:21:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Feb 2018 10:46:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-08"}
