eme\nPREcision Spectrograph, that we estimate will reduce modal-noise-induced RV\nerror to less than 3.2 cm/s.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Feb 2018 20:36:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-21"}
