vity, mainly limited by the satellite jitter, is adapted to detect all\nthe GRBs, localized by the SXI/XGIS, and to acquire spectra for the majority of\nthem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Feb 2018 21:18:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-07"}
