rger than the local flow velocity. We finally discuss the\npractical applications of these effects on the large-scale macroscopic transfer\nand contamination processes caused by microbes in natural environments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Feb 2018 10:41:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Sep 2018 14:21:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-23"}
